description: About this item         No chemicals - Gentle on your baby's skin - Juicy Bumbles reusable nappies are chemical-free. Breathable nappies - No more nappy rash - The reusable nappies are designed to prevent plastic coming into contact with your baby's skin, just our soft bamboo fabric: this allows the baby’s skin to breathe and significantly reduces the risk of nappy rash.     Universal size - The only nappies you need - The Juicy Bumbles reusable nappies are fully adjustable thanks to multiple rows of poppers. You can easily adjust the size of the nappy (i.e. both the waist and the depth). This makes them suitable for use from birth until potty training.     Save a lot of money - Treat yourself or your family - Using reusable nappies can save you more than 1,000 euros from the birth of your baby to when they start toilet training. Just think about what you could do for your family with an extra 1,000 euros.     Help to save the planet - On average, every child will consume the enormous amount of about 6000 disposable nappies, most of which will end up in landfill somewhere. These disposable nappies will take up to 500 years to biodegrade, meaning they will still be on our planet when your baby's great-great-great-great-great-grandson is around. Reusable nappies reduce the amount of 6000 nappies per child to just 12.                See more product details
